data.description: Gorgeous 2 bed, 2.5 bath home in CantaMia at Estrella Mountain Ranch! ***Assumable VA loan at 2.375%*** Beautiful courtyard welcomes you to this open concept floor plan with a spacious great room, upgraded kitchen, and amazing outdoor living space.  Low maintenance landscaping with artificial turf leaves you more time to enjoy the amazing amenities that include the Village Center with fitness center, indoor/outdoor pools & spa, and library plus tennis courts, pickle-ball, bocce ball, and other Estrella amenities that include the Starpointe Residents Club and golf! This home was freshly painted in the spring of 2023. Come check it out today and make this your home before the new year!
